First of all, Deonte (cashier) and Jerome (the cook) were friendly, helpful, and overall amazing. Secondly, Epic Burger is WORTH THE PRICE! Many people complain about the price of these burgers (choice of meat, turkey, chicken, veggie-based, grilled cheese) but the price is higher than most burger places because the meat and ingredients are humanely sourced. The burgers taste juicy, clean, and delicious. Fries are great, both types (potato and sweet potato). And the milkshakes...they're amazing (choice of vanilla, chocolate, strawberry, peanut butter). Perfect to go along with their burgers! Would definitely return to this location and would have epic burger again.
